      "description": "This is a 2007 Mercedes-Benz SLK350 convertible with just under 32,000 miles on it. Black exterior, tan leather interior, and a responsive 3.5L V6 engine that delivers real power. The retractable hardtop means you get the convertible feel with the security of a closed roof when you want it.\n\nRear-wheel drive and a smooth automatic transmission make this a pleasure to drive. You'll get around 17 miles per gallon in the city and 23 on the highway, which is solid for a car built to perform. The mileage is remarkably low for the year, so this one hasn't seen hard use.\n\nCome by and sit in it. Feel the quality of that tan leather and get a sense of how well Mercedes built these. We're here in Villa Park and happy to walk you through what makes this one special.",
